// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1314 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: b316c10d-d610-5123-b5af-0d02a7711806

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.10*")
